{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2ed07e502d","title":"同邓小平关于批评“四人帮”的一次谈话（节录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c056759f18","index":0,"year":1975,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"2ed07e502d","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"四人帮","id":"264b63d816","type":"主题"},{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"刘少奇","id":"3aaab89c2a","type":"人物"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"邓小平","id":"5bd9678625","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"王洪文","id":"8e2c446eb1","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"},{"name":"邓小平","id":"fb776baaf9","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ccfe9e4bbe","type":"title","text":"同邓小平关于批评“四人帮”的一次谈话（节录）","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2ed07e502d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"65408d41e2","type":"paragraph","text":"（邓：会议的情况［注：指一九七五年五月三日主席在政治局会议上批评“四人帮”以后，政治局根据主席指示开会批评“四人帮”的会议。］毛主席都知道了。）","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2ed07e502d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3d676c7323","type":"paragraph","text":"（毛点头）我看有成绩。把问题摆开了。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2ed07e502d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"97d39d58a1","type":"paragraph","text":"（邓：最后他们否认有“四人帮”。）","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2ed07e502d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"352d270762","type":"paragraph","text":"过去有功劳，反刘少奇，反林彪。现在就不行了，反总理，反邓小平，反叶帅，反陈锡联。要告诉庄则栋，有事要找陈锡联，不要跑王洪文、江青，不然陈锡联不好办事。你（指邓）跟庄则栋讲一下，告诉他，不找陈锡联不好。跑江青、王洪文，司令不好办。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2ed07e502d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5269c25583","type":"paragraph","text":"风向快要转了，在政治局。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2ed07e502d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e7fb1ebdeb","type":"paragraph","text":"（邓：政治局的同志气很大，我说不要把话都说完，散了。）","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2ed07e502d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"31654ae10c","type":"paragraph","text":"这个办法好，留有余地。大家清楚就行了。我准备找王洪文谈，叫他找你（指邓），听你的话。他威望不高。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2ed07e502d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"076eec258b","type":"paragraph","text":"（邓：他最后的发言，政治局许多同志感到不真实。）","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2ed07e502d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6e7b7c506a","type":"paragraph","text":"江青也不喜欢他，专门在我这里告他的状。他应该好好工作。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2ed07e502d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fe3f305d1c","type":"paragraph","text":"没有大问题。你要把工作干起来。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2ed07e502d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"37bb979f2f","type":"paragraph","text":"（邓：这方面我还有决心就是了。）那好。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2ed07e502d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"64400937ae","type":"paragraph","text":"（邓：反对的人总有，一定会有。）","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2ed07e502d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1f18cdf9c6","type":"paragraph","text":"（毛笑）木秀于林，风必摧之。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2ed07e502d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"59887903cb","type":"paragraph","text":"（邓：开始工作时，主席给我这个工作岗位，我说主席是把我放在刀尖上了。）","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2ed07e502d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c4f563279b","type":"paragraph","text":"这是叶帅提议的，我赞成的。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2ed07e502d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"55accb4200","type":"paragraph","text":"（邓：总参谋长。）","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2ed07e502d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"04fdc23318","type":"paragraph","text":"就是这样。","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2ed07e502d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"90c48ee257","type":"paragraph","text":"（注：这是中央办公厅秘书局提供的唐闻生、王海容的记录稿。文中的注是原有的。）","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2ed07e502d","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}